7.1 Chat Guard is provided "as is" and "as available," without any warranties of any kind, whether
express, implied, statutory, or otherwise, including but not limited to warranties of
merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement.

7.2 The Licensor does not warrant that Chat Guard will meet the Licensee’s requirements, operate
without interruption, or be free from errors or defects.

8. LIMITATION OF LIABILITY

8.1 To the fullest extent permitted by law, the Licensor shall not be liable for any direct,
indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or exemplary damages, including but not limited to
